%% SBTM — Real-time Data & Event Flow
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant DA as Driver App
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant GPS as gps-tracking
    participant SP as student-presence
    participant EA as emergency-alerts
    participant Q as BullMQ (Redis)
    participant NS as notification-service
    participant FCM as FCM / Twilio / SMTP
    participant WS as Socket.IO hub
    participant AD as Admin Dashboard
    participant PA as Parent App

    Note over DA: Bus in motion (BLE on, GPS on)

    loop Every 3-5 seconds
        DA->>GW: POST /api/v1/location {lat,lng,speed,heading}
        GW->>GPS: forward (JWT verified, school_id set)
        GPS->>GPS: snap-to-road (OSRM), persist location_points
        GPS-->>WS: emit live-location
        WS-->>AD: route live-location update
        WS-->>PA: child route update
    end

    Note over DA: Student boards bus (BLE SmartTag detected)
    DA->>GW: POST /api/v1/student-presence-events
    GW->>SP: forward
    SP->>SP: persist presence_event (BOARD)
    SP-->>WS: emit student-boarded
    WS-->>AD: occupancy update
    WS-->>PA: child boarded notification
    SP->>Q: enqueue notify(parent, BOARD)
    Q->>NS: pull job
    NS->>NS: read prefs + device_tokens
    NS->>FCM: push / sms / email
    NS->>NS: write notification_delivery_log

    Note over DA: Driver presses panic button
    DA->>GW: POST /api/v1/emergency-events {PANIC_BUTTON}
    GW->>EA: forward
    EA->>EA: persist emergency_alert (TIER_1)
    EA-->>WS: emit new-alert
    WS-->>AD: red banner alert
    EA->>Q: enqueue dispatch(school admins)
    Q->>NS: pull job
    NS->>FCM: notify SCHOOL admins (push+sms)

    alt No confirmation in N minutes
        EA->>EA: AUTO_ESCALATED → BOARD
        EA->>Q: enqueue dispatch(BOARD ops)
        Q->>NS: pull
        NS->>FCM: notify BOARD ops
    end

    alt Still unconfirmed
        EA->>EA: escalate → OSTA (TIER_3)
        EA->>Q: enqueue dispatch(OSTA)
        Q->>NS: pull
        NS->>FCM: notify OSTA on-call
    end

    AD->>GW: POST /alerts/:id/confirm
    GW->>EA: confirm
    EA->>EA: status = CONFIRMED · audit log
    EA-->>WS: alert-resolved (or status update)
